cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.PL

The paper deals with the problem of synthesizing controllers for cyber-physical systems, which is a topic in the field of control systems (cs.SY). The use of signal temporal logic (STL) and mixed integer linear programming (MILP) also suggests a connection to logic (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The specific applications mentioned, such as autonomous driving and aircraft electric power systems, suggest a connection to robotics (cs.RO) and programming languages (cs.PL) for specifying and implementing the controllers.
